{"tid":1137795,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尼馬合約有「低價轉會」條款？買斷價1.45億鎊","createTime":"2019-05-04T05:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T07:21:56.000Z","uid":186071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4beefe70caf8dbb1a3081fa8299e59d3e1d8f4dd","tid":1137795,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T05:25:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E5%B0%BC%E9%A6%AC%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84%E6%9C%89-%E4%BD%8E%E5%83%B9%E8%BD%89%E6%9C%83-%E6%A2%9D%E6%AC%BE-223000039--spt.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%25B4%2584%25E6%259C%2589-%25E4%25BD%258E%25E5%2583%25B9%25E8%25BD%2589%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%25AC%25BE-223000039--spt.html&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW9xw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=77df63a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E5%B0%BC%E9%A6%AC%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84%E6%9C%89-%E4%BD%8E%E5%83%B9%E8%BD%89%E6%9C%83-%E6%A2%9D%E6%AC%BE-223000039--spt.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now Sports-體育】巴黎聖日耳門前鋒尼馬差不多每天都有新的離隊傳聞，最近就傳出合約中有一條款，讓他能夠以低價轉會。<br />\n尼馬（Neymar）在2017年以破世界紀錄最高轉會費1.98億鎊，從巴塞隆拿加盟巴黎聖日耳門，但一直有傳他在法國過得並不如意，希望回歸西甲，加盟皇家馬德里。<br />\n西班牙《世界體育報》爆料，指尼馬跟PSG的合約有一項條款，列明當他在球隊踢滿3季後，買斷價立即變成1.45億鎊；即是說在下一個球季後，任何球隊只要付出這個「超抵價」，就可以獲得這名巴西國腳加盟。<br />\n尼馬最近於PSG事事不如意，早前才從重傷中康復，但因為在法國足總盃賽後拳打球迷，有機會被罰停賽8場。他早前已經因為在Instagram爆粗鬧歐聯球證，被歐洲足協罰停賽3場歐洲賽事。"},{"pid":"1809670030745494efe4db4c50780d6fcbbd0704","tid":1137795,"uid":94771,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T05:49:01.000Z","msg":"E條撚斷 一億都比多<br />\n年年2,3月都請事假"},{"pid":"fe81736b293757ffa659651f0636c890a07c4c93","tid":1137795,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:18:50.000Z","msg":"Go mu 同 普爸一決高下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5c639c3144376436324611a3916731d20c922a"